title: Wyclef Jean Interview
itunes:title: Wyclef Jean Interview
description:
Tues 02/07- It's been 20 years since the release of the Score, and Wyclef Jean is still making music for the people. He stopped the Breakfast Club to talk about his new music, some classic stories about the Fugees, where does Lauryn Hill rank amongst the best , what happened to City High and Claudette Ortiz and more. Plus, the crew talked about items that were left from an ex...what do you with them? Sell them? Burn them,? Box the items up? How would you handle that situation?
